&lt;h1 id="genetic-evolution-was-a-prelude-to-memetic-evolution"&gt;Genetic Evolution Was a Prelude to Memetic Evolution&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Oct 20 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideas undergo the same evolutionary process as genes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Popper has a book called &amp;ldquo;Objective Knowledge,&amp;rdquo; and it&amp;rsquo;s subtitled &amp;ldquo;An Evolutionary Approach.&amp;rdquo; And that&amp;rsquo;s no accident, either. There&amp;rsquo;s a symmetry between the theory of epistemology and the theory of evolution as we understand it.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>